OL,3,CFind out which outgoing Jersey
OL,4,Cpoliticians are getting the biggest
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FJersey's government will pay out more
OL,8,Fthan #190,000 in severance payments to
OL,9,FStates Members leaving their positions
OL,10,Ffollowing the election.
OL,12,FThe total sum of #191,432.81 will be
OL,13,Fdivided between 11 departing
OL,14,Fpoliticians, eight of whom stood and
OL,15,Flost their seats in the States
OL,16,FAssembly, while the other three
OL,17,Fvoluntarily stepped down.
OL,19,FLike most jobs, politicians receive a
OL,20,Fseverance payment when they leave
OL,21,Ftheir positions.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
