OL,3,CFind out which outgoing Jersey
OL,4,Cpoliticians are getting the biggest
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FIn the Assembly, members earn a non-
OL,8,Ftaxable "loss of office" payment of
OL,9,Fone month's pay for every four years
OL,10,Fof continuous service if they stand
OL,11,Ffor election and lose.
OL,13,FHowever, politicians who step down
OL,14,Fafter 19 more years of continuous
OL,15,Fservice are also eligible for these
OL,16,Fpayments.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
