CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1782141508
OL,3,CFind out which outgoing Jersey
OL,4,Cpoliticians are getting the biggest
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FThis is because there weren't pension
OL,8,Farrangements in place when those long-
OL,9,Fserving members were elected,
OL,10,Faccording to the States Members'
OL,11,FRemuneration Review.
OL,13,FThose three were Simon Crowcroft,
OL,14,FGeoff Southern, and Deidre Mezbourian,
OL,15,Fwho received #92,577.14 - almost half
OL,16,Fthe total payout money.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
