OL,3,CFind out which outgoing Jersey
OL,4,Cpoliticians are getting the biggest
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FWilliam Millow, Deputy Greffier of the
OL,8,FStates of Jersey, told ITV News that
OL,9,Fsome people had raised concerns about
OL,10,Fthe funds awarded to politicians who
OL,11,Fchoose not to stand for reelection.
OL,13,FHe told ITV News: "On the basis that a
OL,14,Fmonth's salary in 2022 would have been
OL,15,Flower than a month's salary in 2026,
OL,16,Fthen the calculation would lead to a
OL,17,Fhigher sum - the maths and underlying
OL,18,Fprinciple of it would be correct.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1782141508
OL,3,CFind out which outgoing Jersey
OL,4,Cpoliticians are getting the biggest
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,F"However, that hasn't really changed
OL,8,Fin terms of it being based on a
OL,9,Fmonth's salary for a certain length of
OL,10,Fservice."
OL,12,FAn independent review in 2023
OL,13,Frecommended pay rises for States
OL,14,FAssembly members and the current
OL,15,Fremuneration rules.
OL,17,FMr Willow highlighted the fact that
OL,18,Fwhen some of the retiring members
OL,19,Fstarted their jobs in office, there
OL,20,Fwas no pension scheme for States
OL,21,FMembers.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1782141508
OL,3,CFind out which outgoing Jersey
OL,4,Cpoliticians are getting the biggest
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FWhen asked if the rules may change
OL,8,Fbefore the next election, he said that
OL,9,F"they may well do".
OL,11,FPolitical commentator John Henwood
OL,12,Fbelieves that politicians who opt not
OL,13,Fto run again should not be offered any
OL,14,Fextra funds.
OL,16,F"People are retiring, and they are
OL,17,Fgetting golden handshakes", he told
OL,18,FITV News.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1782141508
OL,3,CFind out which outgoing Jersey
OL,4,Cpoliticians are getting the biggest
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,F"If I work in the private sector and
OL,8,Fwe decide to resign, then we are told,
OL,9,F'Thank you very much for your service,
OL,10,Fgoodbye'.
OL,12,F"The notion that States Members, who
OL,13,Fhave served a certain amount of time,
OL,14,Fshould get a golden handshake, will
OL,15,Fnot go down well."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
