OL,3,CFind out which outgoing Jersey
OL,4,Cpoliticians are getting the biggest
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FSimon Crowcroft, the former Connetable
OL,8,Fof St Helier, will receive the most
OL,9,Fmoney of #36,694.06. Although he did
OL,10,Fnot stand in this June's election, he
OL,11,Fis eligible after serving in his
OL,12,Fposition since 2001.
OL,14,FThe next highest sum was #30,311.58 to
OL,15,Fformer St Helier Deputy Geoff
OL,16,FSouthern, and then #25,571.50 to
OL,17,Fdefeated St Saviour Connetable Kevin
OL,18,FLewis.
OL,26,@oD@arryD@Yrr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
