OL,3,CFind out which outgoing Jersey
OL,4,Cpoliticians are getting the biggest
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FThe leader of Reform Jersey, Sam
OL,8,FMezec, is set to receive #15,280.53.
OL,9,FHe dramatically lost his seat after
OL,10,Fchoosing to stand for Senator.
OL,12,FJersey's system differs from the UK's,
OL,13,Fwhere politicians are only eligible
OL,14,Ffor a payout if they stand for re-
OL,15,Felection.
OL,17,FMPs who lose their seats can claim
OL,18,Ffour months' pay and extra funding to
OL,19,Fhelp close down their offices,
OL,20,Fincluding staff redundancy costs.
OL,26,@pD@Brr
