OL,3,CFind out which outgoing Jersey
OL,4,Cpoliticians are getting the biggest
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FIn Guernsey, Deputies who stand for
OL,8,Felection and are not voted back in are
OL,9,Foffered one month's pay.
OL,11,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,12,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,13,FChannel breaks down the key election
OL,14,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,15,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,16,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,17,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,18,FThursday...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/10
